: {"text": "954 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/482794748"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IsOO89tzgx6UcEAMaCDY5NTY5NTE2IKPxoIkGMBc4ywpABnIJNDgyNzk0NzQ4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1630062106.5332987", "card_id": "Q_482695708", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 289}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "泉州警方通报男子因与儿媳发生口角将其杀害，还有哪些信息值得关注？他将承担什么法律后果？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "8 月 26 日，南安市发布警方通报:8 月 21 日，南安市公安局梅山派出所接群众报警，称其妻子侯某雯（女，34 岁，南安市梅山镇人）失踪。我局立即组织开展查找工作。8 月 26 日上午，已找到侯某雯遗体。经初查，犯罪嫌疑人戴某华（男，61 岁，南安市梅山镇人，死者公公）交代了其与儿媳侯某雯发生口角后将其杀害的犯罪事实。戴某华现已被我局依法刑事拘留。目前案件正在进一步审理中，希望广大群众不传谣不造谣，以免对受害者家属造成二次伤害。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-aa0ba35728aae8634242ee9f74fb4246_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "842 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/482695708"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IsOO89tzgx6UcEAMaCDY5NTQ3NjA4IMfVnYkGMEY49QdAB3IJNDgyNjk1NzA4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1630062106.5339832", "card_id": "Q_482367510", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 326}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《喜羊羊与灰太狼》官方放出的拟人图？是什么水平？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-043465941f29b57d5eed41ccd03ba7ac_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "760 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/482367510"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IsOO89tzgx6UcEAMaCDY5NDc0NzI4INC7l4kGMFY4ugZACHIJNDgyMzY3NTEweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1630062106.5346754", "card_id": "Q_480447722", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 89}, "target": {"title_area": {"text"